<p>Hi <span style="text-transform: capitalize"><strong>{{ contactname }}</strong></span>!</p>

<p>Thank you for ordering from The Elba Diaries. Your order confirmation number is <strong>{{ orderid }}</strong> and we
    will get in touch with you shortly to finalize the transaction.</p>

<p>At any time, you can go online to <a href="http://shop.theelbadiaries.com">shop.theelbadiaries.com</a> to review your
    order status or retrieve the order tracking number by clicking on the My Account link located at the top of every
    page.</p>

<p>Your order reads as follows: </p>

<table width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td colspan="4" align="center" bgcolor="#F4EFEB">
            <h2>Order <strong>{{ orderid }}</strong></h2>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr height="30px" style="padding: 10px;">
        <th width="40%">Item Name</th>
        <th width="20%">Unit Price</th>
        <th width="20%">Quantity</th>
        <th width="20%">Total Price</th>
    </tr>
    <tr style="text-align: center; padding: 10px;">
        {{#each items}}
            <td>{{ this.name }}</td>
            <td>{{ this.price }}</td>
            <td>{{ this.quantity }}</td>
            <td>{{ this.totalprice }}</td>
        {{/each}}
    </tr>
    <tr style="padding: 10px;" bgcolor="#F4EFEB">
        <td colspan="3" align="right"><strong>Order Total: </strong></td>
        <td align="center"><strong>{{ totalprice }}</strong></td>
    </tr>
</table>

<table width="100%"
       style="margin:20px 0; padding:20px 0; border-top: 1px solid #979797; border-bottom: 1px solid #979797;">
    <tr>
        <td width="25%" style="border-right: 1px solid #979797">
            <table width="100%">
                <tr>
                    <th>Pickup Date</th>
                </tr>
                <tr align="center">
                    <td>{{ pickupdate }} </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>

        <td width="25%" style="border-right: 1px solid #979797">
            <table width="100%">
                <tr>
                    <th>Pickup Location</th>
                </tr>
                <tr align="center">
                    <td>{{ pickuplocation }}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>

        <td width="25%" style="border-right: 1px solid #979797">
            <table width="100%">
                <tr>
                    <th>Contact Number</th>
                </tr>
                <tr align="center">
                    <td>{{ contactnumber }}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>

        <td width="25%">
            <table width="100%">
                <tr>
                    <th>Instructions</th>
                </tr>
                <tr align="center">
                    <td>{{ instructions }}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p>This completes your order.</p>

<p>Sincerely,</p>
<p> Chastine<br/>Head Baker at The Elba Diaries</p>